From: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Dec 2019 09:51:40 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu/smu: add metrics table lock for vega20 (v2)
Git-commit: 1c455101c6d10c99b310d6bcf613244c97854012
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc5
References: git-fixes

To protect access to the metrics table.

V2: unlock on error

Bug: https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/drm/amd/issues/900
Reviewed-by: Kevin Wang <kevin1.wang@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Evan Quan <evan.quan@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/powerplay/vega20_ppt.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/powerplay/vega20_ppt.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/powerplay/vega20_ppt.c
index 60b9ff097142..0d3a3b0a934e 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/powerplay/vega20_ppt.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/powerplay/vega20_ppt.c
@@ -1678,17 +1678,20 @@ static int vega20_get_metrics_table(struct smu_context *smu,
 	struct smu_table_context *smu_table= &smu->smu_table;
 	int ret = 0;
 
+	mutex_lock(&smu->metrics_lock);
 	if (!smu_table->metrics_time || time_after(jiffies, smu_table->metrics_time + HZ / 1000)) {
 		ret = smu_update_table(smu, SMU_TABLE_SMU_METRICS, 0,
 				(void *)smu_table->metrics_table, false);
 		if (ret) {
 			pr_info("Failed to export SMU metrics table!\n");
+			mutex_unlock(&smu->metrics_lock);
 			return ret;
 		}
 		smu_table->metrics_time = jiffies;
 	}
 
 	memcpy(metrics_table, smu_table->metrics_table, sizeof(SmuMetrics_t));
+	mutex_unlock(&smu->metrics_lock);
 
 	return ret;
 }
